creditline: The Ethel Morrison Van Derlip Fund
medium: Woodblock print (nishiki-e), ink and color on paper
portfolio: Twelve Bouts in the Way of Love (Shikidō torikumi jūniban 色道取組十二番)
text: A couple lies surrounded by robes and bedding, a folding screen in the lower left corner provides some privacy. He kisses her breast and pulls at the opening of her kimono while she covers her mouth with her sleeve, perhaps in embarrassed anticipation.
title: Kissing Her Breast, No. 9 from Twelve Bouts in the Way of Love (Shikidō torikumi jūniban)
